'''''Space Action''''' is a horizontally [[scrolling shooter]] created for the [[Commodore 64]] by Arne Fernlund.<ref name=nsd>{{cite web |url=http://www.nsd.se/nyheter/artikel.aspx?ArticleId=3623147 |title=Fynd från dataspelens stenålder |language=Swedish |accessdate=2011-07-28 |archive-date=2011-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110927100133/http://www.nsd.se/nyheter/artikel.aspx?ArticleId=3623147 |url-status=dead }}</ref> The game took three months to develop and was distributed on cartridge by the Swedish company Handic. More than 10,000 copies were sold world-wide. The game became popular in [[Italy]], where about 7,000 of the copies were sold, and was also a minor success in [[Australia]].<ref name=gameplayer/>

==Legacy==
''Space Action'' made an appearance at an exhibition that the [[Swedish National Museum of Science and Technology]] held in 2008.<ref name=computersweden>{{cite web |url=http://www.idg.se/2.1085/1.141034 |title=Historia och nutid med spel på museum |language=Swedish |accessdate=2011-07-28 |archive-date=2012-10-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121007173408/http://www.idg.se/2.1085/1.141034 |url-status=live }}</ref>

Fernlund did some work on a sequel, ''Space Action 2'', but it was never completed.<ref>{{cite web|title=Space Action 2|url=https://www.gamesthatwerent.com/gtw64/space-action-2/|website=Games That Weren't|date=September 8, 2014|access-date=January 5, 2018|archive-date=January 6, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180106021231/https://www.gamesthatwerent.com/gtw64/space-action-2/|url-status=live}}</ref>

The history behind Fernlund creating ''Space Action'' was featured in the Swedish documentary "Det svenska spelundret" (eng. "The Swedish gaming wonder").<ref>{{Cite episode |title=Varning för barn |episode-link= |url=https://www.svtplay.se/video/32204943/det-svenska-spelundret/det-svenska-spelundret-varning-for-barn?info=visa |access-date=August 18, 2021 |series=Det svenska spelundret |series-link= |first= |last= |network=[[Sveriges Television]] |station= |date=August 18, 2021 |season=1 |number= |time=23:31 |transcript= |transcript-url= |quote= |language=Swedish |archive-date=August 18, 2021 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210818143843/https://www.svtplay.se/video/32204943/det-svenska-spelundret/det-svenska-spelundret-varning-for-barn?info=visa |url-status=live }}</ref>

